      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
        Newcastle's combination of beaches, bushland, and vibrant community makes it one of the best cities in Australia for hobbies. Whether you want to get active, get creative, or get social, there's something here for you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Active Hobbies</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">For people who want to move their bodies and maybe break a sweat:</p>

      <div class="grid gap-4 my-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
