        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">üö¥ Cycling</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-2">The Fernleigh Track and coastal paths offer scenic rides. Road cycling groups meet regularly for social rides.</p>
