        <p class="text-green-700 mb-4">Your first session at Newcastle PCYC Table Tennis Club is free. No booking, no commitment ‚Äî just show up and see if you like it.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/timetable" class="bg-green-600 text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-md font-medium hover:bg-green-700 transition">See the Timetable</a>
